name: Harukaze Doremi (Ojamajo Doremi)
description:
Harukaze Doremi from Ojamajo Doremi, the first magical girl franchise in my childhood.

Right now we only have LoRA with her casual outfit, her witch outfit will train and be uploaded later.

CASUAL OUTFIT:

use hrkzdrm_cs to summon her, uses red hair, double bun, musical note hair ornament to form her head, use hood, pink vest, pink shorts, belt to summon her casual outfit

WITCH OUTFIT:

Use hrkzdrm_mgc to summon her, use hair bun, short hair, red hair, pink eyes, witch hat, jewelry, earrings to form her head, use pink dress, skirt, puffy sleeves, pink gloves to summon her outfit.

Use Casual outfit version if you plan to make her wear something differently.

You need closed mouth, smile if you want her little smile, since she loves to :D.
